203d2b24a5bc5183","tid":25882,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>陳偉霆上到位唔知點解幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢以前真係柒既<br />\n<br />\n但唔算好乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫完Baby講高過你之後<br />\n<br />\n仲要慘被Baby come on William<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家出返啖氣唔駛再比黃曉明問是誰<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘成個亞洲黎講佢依家仲紅過黃曉明<br />\n<br />\n起碼去到韓國有成班人接機<br />\n<br />\n黃曉明頂盡咪中國入面圍爐打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個油頭粉面又增高墊，鬼上到大台咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾勵志， 黃曉明食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到韓國有成班人接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩事係果邊紅到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef5928beef591ba949fd0dd05f9a2460d680a77","tid":25882,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到韓國有成班人接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩事係果邊紅到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓星熱潮席捲全球眾所周知，不過最近終於有突破。繼之前王大陸成功攻佔韓國市場後，估不到港仔陳偉霆（William）亦達成反攻韓國壯舉，剛在北京完成巡迴演唱會發佈會的陳偉霆，日前便遠赴韓國取景拍MV，有指今次製作費高達7位數。雖然飛機延誤達兩小時，但當他步出離境大堂時，竟立即被過百女粉絲包圍，為答謝粉絲苦待，陳偉霆亦識做同粉絲沿路傾偈。他更即席用韓文同大家打招呼：「大家好，我是陳偉霆」每講一句，現場韓妹亦尖叫不絕，很神奇！<br />\n<br />\n其實William憑《古劍奇譚》、《少年四大名捕》在內地打開知名度後，去年更打入福布斯中國名人榜。<span style=\"color: red;\">之後《少年四大名捕》在韓國播出，更令他在韓國上位</span>，成為去年亞洲音樂節中唯一有份出席的中國歌手，在音樂節中又用韓文唱《love u 2》，冧死台下韓國粉絲。唔知黃曉明，現在還知不知道誰是陳偉霆呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/32768/-%E8%80%8C%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E9%9C%86%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%BF%BD%E7%84%B6%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1-%E6%8A%B5%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%96%E5%8F%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F32768%2F-%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259C%2586%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E7%2584%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2586%25B1-%25E6%258A%25B5%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%2588%25BE%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B0%2596%25E5%258F%25AB&d=594jwF06iYRaoK%2BpvQI4GHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c48c58e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/32768/-%E8%80%8C%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E9%9C%86%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%BF%BD%E7%84%B6%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1-%E6%8A%B5%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%96%E5%8F%AB</a></span>"},{"pid":"4a54d69cc34a39f6823ea856cba949605aab9a7b","tid":25882,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:28:46.000Z","msg":"究竟佢衰咩要比人反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53318db07e18b37559d049870652d5caf1df4a85","tid":25882,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陳偉霆上到位唔知點解幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢以前真係柒既<br />\n但唔算好乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n幫完Baby講高過你之後<br />\n仲要慘被Baby come on William<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br